title: Nara Rohit’s next titled Tuntari
text:
Nara Rohit is currently busy with a couple of movies which are shaping up to hit the screens later next year. And he's also gearing up for the remake of Tamil super hit Maan Karate. According to the latest update, the film has been titled Tuntari and the first look posters which were released showcase a fresh look of the film. Rohit plays a boxer in this romantic entertainer which is helmed by Kumar Nagendra.
